content.text: Trial 4/5, Stage 'ytraverse2': Please describe the image and compute the stiffness matrix.

The image shows a 3D printed structure with a groove. The red circle highlights a section of the groove oriented along the Y-axis.

**Assumptions for the Stiffness Matrix:**
1. High stiffness along Y to support traversal.
2. X and Z directions maintain lower stiffness.
